TCBY Enterprises Inc said itsboard has approved a three-for-two split of its common stockwith a distribution to be made on April 24 to stockholders ofrecord on April 9.    The split will increase the number of outstanding shares toover 26 mln from about 17.3 mln shares now, the company said.    TCBY Enetrprises is a franchisor and operator of retailstores specializing in frozen yogurt-related treats. Reuter&#3;